title: [1970] Freddie Hubbard - Red Clay (320kbps)
description:
1970 fusion style album from Freddie Hubbard with a fantastic band including Herbie Hancock on piano, Ron Carter on bass, Lenny White on drums, & Joe Henderson on tenor saxophone. This was ripped from a remastered CD in 320kbps. Includes a bonus track, Red Clay (Live Version), with George Benson on guitar, Stanley Turrentine on tenor saxophone, Johnny Hammond on organ & electric piano, Billy Cobham on drums, & Aitro Moreira on percussion.

05. Cold Turkey               [10:25 ]
